snippet: The medical series "House" will come to an end this season, the show's producers and the Fox network announced Wednesday.
abstract: The medical series "House" will come to an end this season, the show's producers and the Fox network announced Wednesday.
lead_paragraph: One of the most popular and highly regarded television dramas of the last decade, the medical series "House," will come to an end this season, the show's producers and the Fox network announced Wednesday.

headline.main: After Eight Seasons, 'House' Slated to End
